{{hebrew_title| |אימץ| |Verbs/Index|Contents}}
==Verb Overview==
'''Definition:''' to adopt (a child); to take responsibility for, to foster; to adopt, to espouse (idea, concept, plan); to strengthen, to consolidate, to reinforce
<p><br>
{{Hebrew/Verb|Adopt; Strengthen; Strain|אִימֵּץ
 | adopt | מְאַמֵּץ | אִימּוּץ | שלמים | פִּיעֵל | לְאַמֵּץ | אמץ
}}
